title: JB KeyState v2.1.3.10
description:
JB KeyState v2.1.3.10 - a must have for users of keyboard&#039;s with no status led&#039;s.

A small application that show the state of the Caps, Scroll & Num using window, trayicon & sound.
It is customizable with many options, set or force any state is also possible.

languages: English & Norwegian.

Changelog:


KeyState v2.1.3.10:
Added png image support.
Added Ability to Play typewritersound or any sound on all or selected keys.
Added Ability to display when selected key(s) is pressed (with a popupwindow).
Some other minor bugfixes.

Setup v1.0.2.10
Fixed UAC incompatibility & windows vista installation problems.

KeyState v2.1.2.76:
Reenabled theme support lost due to an error editing resources in JbKeyState.exe.
Removed transparent background on new main startup-screen (ugly on dark backgrounds).

Setup v1.0.1.16:
Fixed error overwriting files when keystate is closed during installation (i hope).
It is strongly reccomended that you exit the KeyState program before you start the keystate setup program.

KeyState v2.1.2.75:
Fixing error on no more response when showing exit-application question-box.
Changed startupscreen.

Please note that the Readme Vista Users information might also apply to some windows xp users.

Windows 98 Users might want to use Version 1 of the Keystate program, due to some incompatibility with the
color-palette & resoultion used in keystate v2.
